{
  "title": "A Network State to Regenerate the Earth @ETHDenver 🌐 🌱 | Roundup #54",
  "slug": "roundup-54",
  "html": "<p><strong>Sporky greetings, regens! 👋 </strong><em>(EthDenver joke for those not in the know!)</em></p><p><em>I am <a href=\"https://t.co/EbllE8ZTT8\">Susana González</a>, content creator and head of partnerships for <a href=\"https://impactscope.com\">ImpactScope</a> in LATAM, and a strong believer of knowledge sharing through deep story telling. It is my pleasure to knit a new Refi web for this week! </em></p><p><em>In this week's edition, we'll be diving into a ReFi recap of ETH Denver, the announcement of a ReFi Network State, + the top news, events, and jobs from the ReFi world and beyond. Let's jump right in. </em></p><hr><h1 id=\"refi-at-ethdenver-%F0%9F%8C%B1-%F0%9F%8C%B3-%F0%9F%9A%80\">ReFi at ETHDenver! 🌱 🌳 🚀</h1><p><a href=\"https://www.ethdenver.com/\">ETHDenver</a> is one of the most hotly awaited events in the Web3 space. This year was no exception, the #<a href=\"https://academy.binance.com/en/glossary/buidl\">BUIDL</a> spirit was in the air. One difference? --&gt; The ever growing presence of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23RegenerativeFinance\">Regenerative Finance</a> community, here are some highlights! 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/regenerate-earth-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/03/regenerate-earth-1.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/03/regenerate-earth-1.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/regenerate-earth-1.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"a-network-state-to-regenerate-the-earth-%F0%9F%8C%B1%F0%9F%8C%90\">A Network State to Regenerate the Earth 🌱🌐</h2><p>Our very own <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climatexcrypto?s=11&amp;t=mHLye05ZUet5stiYo4ra0A\">John Ellison </a>was jamming in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MentholProtocol/status/1630251504820011009?t=hbMubf6raiDUc31WS_vtMg&amp;s=19\">events</a> throughout the week from Flowcarbon's <a href=\"https://twitter.com/weareflowcarbon/status/1631328662711840769?s=20\">Climate Summit</a> to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg/status/1631787205856460801?s=20\">Carbonpath's event with Celo</a> and frens. The peak was his headline talk unveiling ReFi DAO's mission to create a network state to regenerate the earth rooted in local startup communities around the world. Check out more details below..</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ICYMI<br><br>A network state to regenerate the earth—rooted in local startup communities around the world. <br><br>Each community has its own token, it’s own treasury and its own unique vision of regeneration. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24REFI&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$REFI</a> is the reserve asset that brings it all together &amp; coordinates action. <a href=\"https://t.co/d5k1IPFnIp\">https://t.co/d5k1IPFnIp</a></p>&mdash; jE in Denver (@climateXcrypto) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto/status/1632400261799899139?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 5, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Want to learn more and see what the new ReFi Nation might look and feel like? Come join at the next <a href=\"https://lu.ma/refi-lisboa-2\">ReFi Lisboa Event — Emergence</a>...</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/X5eVP7ssCYw?start=20&feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"ReFi Lisboa KICK-OFF! 🎉\"></iframe></figure><p>+ check out this snippet from the last <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiLisboa\">ReFi Lisboa</a> event.. 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">&#39;Everybody gotta win&#39; - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MartinGQ?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@MartinGQ</a> 🚀<br><br>Regeneration is crucial for the survival of our planet and the actions we take today will determine the state of our environment for generations to come 🌱 <a href=\"https://t.co/wo1HOhzdFp\">pic.twitter.com/wo1HOhzdFp</a></p>&mdash; ReFi Lisboa | Mar 23 🗓️ (@ReFiLisboa) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiLisboa/status/1630855532558036993?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 1, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/refi-lisboa-2\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Apply to attend</a></div><p>Make sure to <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/#/portal/signup\">subscribe</a> for more alpha and updates on the ReFi Nation coming very soon! Also please do share to anyone else who might also be interested 🙏</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/#/portal/signup\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Subscribe for Updates</a></div><h2 id=\"snippets-from-regenlandia-%E2%9B%B0%EF%B8%8F\">Snippets from Regenlandia ⛰️</h2><p>Regenlandia - a new dedicated space for Regens @ETHDenver - was full of ideas, booths, and people tinkering on innovative ReFi solutions. If you missed out, don't worry! --&gt; You can still check out the recording on <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/ethereumdenver\">Twitch</a> or <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@ETHDenver/videos\">Youtube</a>. Here are some sessions worth watching:</p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcusdotam\">Marcus</a> from <a href=\"https://ethereum.org/en/foundation/\">Ethereum Foundation</a> talks about Ethereum enhancing public good for global coordination and enhancement for the future of human civilization.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/P9z0GeENaOs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"Ethereum for the Next Billion\"></iframe></figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ManuAlzuru\">Manu</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DoinGudHQ\">DoinGud</a> discusses the challenges with impact communities and purpose-driven DAOs .</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mGEMOdbb9b8?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"The problems with DAOs, Impact Communities and purpose driven projects\"></iframe></figure><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/rxdha1\">Ridha</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CyberpantherPRT\">CyberPantherZ</a> talks about the concept of “The System of Good”, a trustless unstoppable secure ideal that we can all support and implement using smart contracts.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5UgRPL8y3FQ?start=892&feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"Paying It Forward: Inclusivity in Web3 &amp; The System of Good\"></iframe></figure><p>+ here are some other highlighted talks and moments: </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">One of my favourity presentations at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EthereumDenver?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@EthereumDenver</a> by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NEARProtocol?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@NEARProtocol</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mariekeflament?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@mariekeflament</a>. We need <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/diversity?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#diversity</a> of thought &amp; languages in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Web3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Web3</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> to make it both local &amp; mainstream. Crucially, we need <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/integrity?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#integrity</a>. Would ur granny be proud of what ur doing? It so resonates with me. <a href=\"https://t.co/r7emUNFY3I\">pic.twitter.com/r7emUNFY3I</a></p>&mdash; carapilla.eth (@Carapilla) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Carapilla/status/1632395832493510656?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 5, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">“The technology itself doesn’t change anything. It’s the way we use the technology.” <br>- <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jori_armbruster?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@jori_armbruster</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EthicHub?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@EthicHub</a> on his panel Understanding the Regeneration on Regenerative Finance. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/CeloDenver?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#CeloDenver</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ETHDenver?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ETHDenver</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/prosperityforall?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#prosperityforall</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/DDStCJecqs\">pic.twitter.com/DDStCJecqs</a></p>&mdash; Celo (@CeloOrg) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg/status/1631807187411501058?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 4, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The Impact &amp; Public Goods stage at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EthereumDenver?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@EthereumDenver</a> is literally bringing me to tears today.<br><br>&quot;The biggest opportunity we have in web3 is to redesign what it means to be human&quot;. <a href=\"https://t.co/NCD9p6lwCk\">pic.twitter.com/NCD9p6lwCk</a></p>&mdash; Lauren Luz | karmaticacid.eth in Denver (@karmaticacid) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/karmaticacid/status/1632076356962906112?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 4, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"climate-summit-was-a-blast-%F0%9F%8E%89\">Climate Summit was a blast! 🎉</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.climatesummit.world/\">Climate Summit</a> is a two-day side event at ETHDenver dedicated to the most important things, how ReFi can make a difference for Climate change and finding the intersection of carbon markets, ESG, sustainability, and Web3. Here are some of the actions taking place:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">A key realization from the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EthereumDenver?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@EthereumDenver</a> 2023 Climate Summit as we wrap up: <br><br>Theres a LOT of work to do to create a world where regenerative finance permeates into our economic systems &amp; global climate solutions- but how is a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/forest?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#forest</a> measured?<br><br>➡️One tree at a time<br>Stay tuned! <a href=\"https://t.co/b9hQSlu8nV\">pic.twitter.com/b9hQSlu8nV</a></p>&mdash; Open Forest Protocol (OFP) @ ETH Denver (@OpenForest_) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OpenForest_/status/1631085696147681280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 2, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Some important insights from a fascinating panel on the Future of Forward Financing:<br><br>“The capital needs have historically not been met in the climate space,” — Mehul Bhagat, Elea Ventures <a href=\"https://t.co/W1FHt93qhX\">pic.twitter.com/W1FHt93qhX</a></p>&mdash; Flowcarbon (@weareflowcarbon) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/weareflowcarbon/status/1631073385407995905?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 1, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">planning how to bring the next billion users into <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/web3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#web3</a> with a dream all-female panel at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EthDenver?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#EthDenver</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ClimateSummit?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ClimateSummit</a> <br><br>thank you <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CeloOrg</a> for having us 🤩 <a href=\"https://t.co/3B3oxSYk6Z\">pic.twitter.com/3B3oxSYk6Z</a></p>&mdash; calanthia.soul (@calanthiaaa) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/calanthiaaa/status/1631023759086714880?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 1, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>Does it feel like the energy and momentum around ReFi is surging at the moment? It sure does to me... LFGrow 🌱 💚 🚀</p><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-newsbites-%F0%9F%97%9E%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi NewsBites 🗞️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emthe-latest-updates-across-refi-twitter-and-beyondem\"><em>The latest updates across ReFi Twitter and beyond...</em></h3></div><h2 id=\"united-nations-agree-on-a-historic-treaty-to-protect-ocean-life-%F0%9F%8C%8A\">United Nations Agree on a Historic Treaty to Protect Ocean Life! 🌊</h2><p>The new treaty would make it possible to create marine-protected areas and enact other conservation measures on the 'high seas' - the immense expanse of ocean covering almost half the world. Big win to celebrate for the planet 🎉</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The <a href=\"https://twitter.com/UN?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@UN</a> Ocean Treaty has just been signed by nearly 200 countries! 🌊🌊🌊<br><br>Huge win for the ocean and the planet as a whole, but only a step on a long climb!<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ClimateChange?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ClimateChange</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/UNTreaty?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#UNTreaty</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/OceanBiodiversity?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#OceanBiodiversity</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/05DQAG8OIl\">https://t.co/05DQAG8OIl</a></p>&mdash; Kolektivo (@Kolektivo) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Kolektivo/status/1632375201437474817?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 5, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"gold-standard-announces-carbon-tokenisation-consultation-with-key-refi-players\">Gold Standard Announces Carbon Tokenisation Consultation with key ReFi players!</h2><p>This month, Gold Standard will initiate a readiness phase of a new model for digital carbon asset creation. This will include structured consultations with a range of organisations, including Web3 ReFi orgs <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ToucanProtocol\">Toucan</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/weareflowcarbon\">Flowcarbon</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thallo_io\">Thallo</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/earthchainuk\">Earthchain</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Bitgreen_\">Bitgreen</a>! The aim is to explore best practice principles to leverage the advantages of distributed ledger technologies as well as safeguards to avoid perverse incentives, double counting, or other risks. We look forward to hearing the results 🚀</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">In a huge step forward for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/goldstandard?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@goldstandard</a> announced formal partnerships with five <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Web3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Web3</a> organizations, kicking off the next stage in the process of creating effective and inclusive digital assets linked to its carbon credits.<br><br>Learn more here: <a href=\"https://t.co/QpIYQhXrMT\">https://t.co/QpIYQhXrMT</a> 2/7</p>&mdash; KlimaDAO (@KlimaDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KlimaDAO/status/1632697441873981440?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 6, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"beach-collective-youth-advisory-board-%E2%98%80%EF%B8%8F\">Beach collective Youth Advisory Board ☀️ </h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/beach_token\">Beach collective ($Beach</a>) is looking for young regens to join the newly formed youth advisors for their Beach Action platform.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://beachtoken.io/blog/launching-our-youth-advisory-boardhttps://beachtoken.io/blog/launching-our-youth-advisory-board\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/image-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1126\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/03/image-1.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/03/image-1.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/03/image-1.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/03/image-1.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://beachtoken.io/blog/launching-our-youth-advisory-board\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Share with friends and fam!</a></div><h2 id=\"also-on-our-radar-this-week\">Also on our radar this week</h2><ul><li>🤓 <a href=\"https://go.gitcoin.co/blog/regenerative-web-3-the-landscape-opportunities-and-entry-points\">Get to know the Regenerative Web3 - The Landscape, Opportunites, and Entry Points</a></li><li><strong>📲</strong><a href=\"https://cointelegraph.com/news/celo-president-rene-reinsberg-explains-why-the-protocol-is-optimizing-for-mobile\">Celo's Rene Reinsberg explains why the protocol is optimizing for mobile</a></li></ul><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"%F0%9F%94%A5-projects-of-the-week\">🔥 Projects of the Week</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"ema-showcase-of-top-voted-projects-from-the-refi-dao-websiteem\"><em>A showcase of top voted projects from the ReFi DAO website!</em></h3><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View More</a></div><p>Top 5 most-voted projects of the week at <a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/ecosystem/organizations\">refidao.com</a>:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/ecosystem/organizations\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/image-5.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/03/image-5.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/03/image-5.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/03/image-5.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/03/image-5.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><ol><li>🔧 <strong><a href=\"https://impactscope.com/\">ImpactScope</a></strong>: Helps organizations deploy web3 tools to measure, verify and amplify their impact.</li><li>☁️ <strong><a href=\"https://www.dclimate.net/\">dClimate</a></strong>: The First Decentralized Network for Climate Data.</li><li>🛖 <strong><a href=\"https://www.kolektivo.network/\">Kolektivo</a></strong>: enables local communities to create and manage their own regenerative economy to fuel prosperity.</li><li>🪸 <strong><a href=\"https://newatlantis.io/\">New Atlantis</a></strong>: Ocean regen DAO focused on aligning value creation with improvements in the health of the oceans.</li><li>🌎 <strong><a href=\"https://www.openearth.org/\">Open Earth Foundation</a></strong>: Open source tech for planet Earth Building digital architecture to scale climate action.</li></ol><p><em><em><em><em>*Projects included in </em></em></em><a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/roundup-53/\"><em><em><em>roundup #5</em></em>3<em><em> </em></em></em></a><em><em><em>are not counted this week!</em></em></em></em></p><p><strong>Votes have now been reset</strong> so head over to <a href=\"refidao.com\">refidao.com</a>, make an account, and show some support to your favourite projects in the ecosystem this week! 💚</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/ecosystem/organizations\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Vote away!</a></div><hr><h3 id=\"add-your-refi-project-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi Project! 👇🏽</h3><p><em>Have a project you want to add to our database? Click the button below to submit an application!</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/submit-project\" class=\"kg-btn kg-bt