card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://podfollow.com/refi-podcast/view\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Listen to the episode</a></div><h2 id=\"other-%F0%9F%94%A5-podcasts-on-our-radar\">Other 🔥 Podcasts on our Radar:</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cryptoaltruism.org/blog/crypto-altruism-podcast-episode92-impactscope-supporting-the-un-sustainable-development-goals-with-web3-solutions\"><strong>ImpactScope - Supporting the UN Sustainable Development Goals with Web3 solutions </strong></a><strong> 🌱| Crypto Altruism by Drew Simon</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RsgEGCRU5vI\">“Banner Blindness” and the Future of Privacy &amp; Tracking on the Internet</a><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RsgEGCRU5vI\"> </a></strong> 🕵️</strong>| <strong>Brains Byte Back with Chris Smith 💡</strong> </li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ebathJUIWHk\"><strong>\"Brave new World\" Jax Davey, Founder of Nuevo: On a Mission to Build the World's Most Purpose Driven Agency</strong></a><strong> 🌍</strong>| <strong>Bruce Weaver</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"https://www.buzzsprout.com/1918037/12321756\">Creating Green Currency with Beach Collective's Robert Cobbold</a> 🏝</strong>| <strong>The nature Backed Podcast</strong></li></ul><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-events-%F0%9F%AA%A9\">ReFi Events 🪩</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emget-your-refi-on-with-friends-in-person-and-onlineem\"><em>Get your ReFi on with friends in-person and online...</em></h3><a href=\"https://refispring.com/\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View more</a></div><h1 id=\"looking-forward-%F0%9F%93%8D\">Looking Forward 📍</h1><p><em>Some of the exciting