traland): <em><a href=\"https://twitter.com/theaeternals\">TheAeternals</a> organized and amazing metaverse event and it was my first time inside it! </em></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Having a great time in Decentraland!   Come join in .... details below:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MetaverseReFiWeek?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#MetaverseReFiWeek</a>!<br><br>Kicked off yesterday with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/theaeternals?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@theaeternals</a><br> :)<br><br>Join us all week for some amazing talks on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Impact?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Impact</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFTs?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NFTs</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Web3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Web3</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/qcfTmDKIQL\">https://t.co/qcfTmDKIQL</a><br>Realm: DG. 40/-40<a href=\"https://twitter.com/creatorlabsX?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@creatorlabsX</a></p>&mdash; Derreck Landon (@pines_five) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/pines_five/status/1630638055559184388?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 28, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>It was more complicated than I expected but more fun than I imagined! It is a universe, so you have to walk and find the places you are to attend! Caribbean Plaza wasn't that difficult to find, but boy getting around the elevator was! 😅</p><p>Have a look at this clip of me talking (&amp; dancing!) about dynamic NFTs and other ways to make an impact in Web3 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I got to participate in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MetaverseReFiWeek?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#MetaverseReFiWeek</a> in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/decentraland?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@decentraland</a> my first time in the metaverse and it was as scary as you can imagine. <br><br>Thank you so much to 🥳<a href=\"https://twitter.com/theaeternals?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@theaeternals</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Gallardo_Luchi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Gallardo_Luchi</a> <br><br>We got to talk or dance about <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ImpactScope?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ImpactScope</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OrelliRafaella?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@OrelliRafaella</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MadhuriRahman?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@MadhuriRahman</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/rTkz2pfHGv\">pic.twitter.com/rTkz2pfHGv</a></p>&mdash; Susana González (@SuaNex) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SuaNex/status/1631643353338068993?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 3, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p>The week continues, <a href=\"https://medium.com/@theAEternals/how-to-access-metaverse-refi-week-on-decentraland-1228d63c2c9\">and you can join </a>other events too - see you there!</p><hr><h2 id=\"add-your-refi-event-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi event! 👇🏽</h2><p><em>Got a ReFi, crypto, or climate event coming up and what to have it featured in the newsletter? Add yours to ReFi Spring! </em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://airtable.com/shrKUM3uH0Ph5oEYw\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Add your ReFi event</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-4.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-4.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-jobs-%F0%9F%91%A9%F0%9F%8F%BD%E2%80%8D%F0%9F%9A%80\">ReFi Jobs 👩🏽‍🚀</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emfind-your-next-gig-at-a-leading-refi-ventureem\"><em>Find your next gig at a 